### Health check
GET http://localhost:3001/

### Get all employees
GET http://localhost:3001/employees

### Search
GET http://localhost:3001/employees?q=ahmad

### Sort by salary descending
GET http://localhost:3001/employees?sortBy=salary&order=desc

### Create new employee
POST http://localhost:3001/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "empId": "EMP099",
  "name": "Test Employee",
  "email": "test.employee@company.com.my",
  "department": "IT",
  "position": "Intern",
  "hireDate": "2024-01-01",
  "salary": 1800,
  "active": true
}

### Update (use the id returned from the POST above)
PUT http://localhost:3001/employees/8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "empId": "EMP099",
  "name": "Test Employee Updated",
  "email": "test.employee@company.com.my",
  "department": "HR",
  "position": "Executive",
  "hireDate": "2024-01-01",
  "salary": 3500,
  "active": true
}

### Delete
DELETE http://localhost:3001/employees/8